ZH: 夫人，您好！
EN: Madam, hello!

ZH: 请问，这位夫人需要帮助吗？
EN: Excuse me, does this lady need any assistance?

ZH: 我的夫人是一位非常温柔的人。
EN: My wife is a very gentle person.

ZH: 这位夫人是我们公司的总经理。
EN: This lady is the general manager of our company.

ZH: 夫人和先生正在度假。
EN: The madam and her husband are on vacation.

ZH: 这本是夫人最喜欢的小说。
EN: This book is the lady's favorite novel.

ZH: 夫人要参加一个重要会议。
EN: The Madam is going to attend an important conference.

ZH: 请向夫人道歉，因为这是我的过错。
EN: Please apologize to the lady, as it is my fault.

ZH: 夫人的品味非常高雅。
EN: The madam has a very refined taste.

ZH: 夫人对于艺术充满热情。
EN: The lady is passionate about art.

ZH: 请注意，夫人的意见非常重要。
EN: Please note that the lady's opinion is very important.

ZH: 夫人保持着优雅的风度。
EN: The madam maintains an elegant demeanor.

ZH: 这是夫人的座位。
EN: This is the lady's seat.

ZH: 请夫人务必签字确认。
EN: Please madam, make sure to sign and confirm.

ZH: 我会立即向夫人汇报。
EN: I will report to the madam immediately.

ZH: 请夫人前去VIP休息室。
EN: Please madam, proceed to the VIP lounge.

ZH: 夫人是我们酒店的贵宾。
EN: The lady is a VIP at our hotel.

ZH: 夫人善解人意而又谦虚。
EN: The madam is understanding and humble.

ZH: 这是夫人的手表，非常精致。
EN: This is the lady's watch, very delicate.

ZH: 夫人要求保密此信息。
EN: The madam requests that this information remains confidential.
